Class EDIFHierPortInst

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif.EDIFHierPortInst

  • public class EDIFHierPortInst
extends Object
    Combines an EDIFHierPortInst with a full hierarchical instance name to uniquely identify a port instance in a netlist. Created on: Sep 12, 2017
